subject: Competition Launch: Santa 2025 - Christmas Tree Packing Challenge
snippet: Hi Phishypro, Santa's sleigh is loaded but there's a tiny problem - his Christmas tree toys won't all fit in the boxes! This year, your mission is to help Santa find the smallest square box
body:
Kaggle








Hi Phishypro,

Santa's sleigh is loaded but there's a tiny problem - his Christmas tree  
toys won't all fit in the boxes!

This year, your mission is to help Santa find the smallest square box that  
can hold shipments of 1 to 200 tiny trees. Think of it as the ultimate  
optimization puzzle because the smaller the box, the happier the elves (and  
Rudolph)!





Total Prizes:

$50,000


Entry Deadline:

January 23, 2026




Learn More



So grab your coding sleigh, fire up your algorithms, and help Santa pack  
his trees perfectly for delivery across the globe! The best solution will  
earn not only the grand prize but also a nod from the big guy himself.  
Plus, early entries might even receive a special $10,000 reward from  
Rudolph!

Happy packing!

Walter Reade
Kaggle Data Scientist



Kaggle, Inc 1600 Amphitheatre Pkwy Mountain View, CA 94043

This email was sent to prophishy@gmail.com because you indicated that you'd  
like to receive news and updates about Kaggle. If you don't want to receive  
these emails in the future, please unsubscribe here. You can also change  
your preferences on your account's profile page by logging in at kaggle.com.
